paths: Obvious exits: northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest
description: This central area is cleaner than the surrounding tunnels.  Relatively fresh straw covers the ground and in one corner is a tiny mound of partly digested cloudberry seeds.  The walls are old and full of small holes and cracks -- with a bit of effort you might be able to climb them.
title: [Infested Tunnels, Rat's Nest]
